thumb|right|judy garland and chorus perform " the trolley song " in meet me in st. louis " the trolley song " is a song written by hugh martin and ralph blane and made famous by judy garland in the 1944 film meet me in st. louis .

films of the ' 40s : judy garland sang " the trolley song " & " have yourself a merry little christmas " in this hit musical

